casebody.data:
Marie Therese ASSA'AD-FALTAS, petitioner,
v.
Tandy CARTER, et al. No. 16-329. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 28, 2016.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for a writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United State Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
